Once you have been given access to the bbgpu QOS, then you need to add this to your job submission script:
#SBATCH --qos bbgpu

And, also you have to specify the type of GPU to send your job too:
    Nvidia Tesla P100 (#SBATCH --gres gpu:p100:1)
    Nvidia Tesla K20 (#SBATCH --gres gpu:k20:1)
    Nvidia Quadro 5000 (#SBATCH --gres gpu:q5000:1)


Regards,
Simon
